abstract: The Rogue Hybrid offers an even more fuel-efficient version of a compact sport utility vehicle that was already stingy with a gallon of gas.
snippet: The Rogue Hybrid offers an even more fuel-efficient version of a compact sport utility vehicle that was already stingy with a gallon of gas.
lead_paragraph: TRENDS ebb and flow in the automotive world. A decade back, being seen in a Prius was très chic. Now, with gasoline cheaper than bottled water, Americans are accessorizing their driveways with S.U.V.s and crossovers.

headline.main: Video Review: Nissan’s Rogue Joins the Toyota RAV4’s Hybrid S.U.V. Club
headline.print_headline: Not as Efficient as a Prius,  but a Lot More Fashionable
